overview: Our rainy day adventure to the Titanic Artifact Exhibition in Orlando, Fl Join us as we make our way through the exhibit and examine genuine Titanic artifacts recovered from the wreckage on the seabed; learn about the history behind them. All artifact and historical information provided by the Orlando Titanic Artifact Exhibition. All film footage shot on site in Orlando, Florida Narrated by: Quentin Deckard
title: Titanic Documentary The Artifact Exhibition
